									Services
								     **************


- Create the mongo service and deployment :
  
    $ kubectl create -f mongo-deployment.yml 
    $ kubectl create -f mongo-service.yml 


- list the service creation :

    $ kubectl get svc 

-  Create the nodejs service and deployment :

    $ kubectl create -f nodejs-deployment.yml 
    $ kubectl create -f nodejs-service.yml 

- ndescription of service :
  
    $ kubectl describe svc mongo

- Access the node.js application :

    $ minikube ip

- Access the application in the browser :
 
     minikubeIp:targetprot

- display all object of cluster :
 
     $ kubectl get all

- Access from outside the cluster => got browser :
  
       minikubeIp:nodePort

     
